9cor sym\u00e9trique compos\u00e9 de rinceaux, d\u0027oiseaux et d\u0027un troph\u00e9e d\u0027armes. Une \u00e9chelle gradu\u00e9e de 1 \u00e0 7 permet de mesurer l\u0027amplitude des oscillations. Echappement \u00e0 verge et fus\u00e9e avec cha\u00eene.","inscriptions":"Signature : \r ; mouvement sign\u00e9 : BALTAZAR MARTINOT\/A PARIS","namesAndTitles":"","onomastics":"","dimension":[{"type":"Hauteur","value":"7,6","displayDimension":"7,6 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":1,"note":""},{"type":"Diam\u00e8tre","value":"5,7","displayDimension":"5,7 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":2,"note":""},{"type":"Epaisseur","value":"3,2","displayDimension":"3,2 cm","unit":"cm","anteriorPrecision":"","posteriorPrecision":"","tri":3,"note":""}],"shape":"","materialsAndTechniques":"Mat\u00e9riau : laiton\r\nMat\u00e9riau : or\r\nTechnique : techniques m\u00e9tal (orf\u00e8vrerie)\r\nMat\u00e9riau : peau = cuir","placeOfCreation":"Paris (France-\u003EIle-de-France = Ile de France)","dateOfDiscovery":"","placeOfDiscovery":"","provenance":"","historicalContext":[],"objectHistory":"Collection Claudius C\u00f4te (1881-1956), Lyon ; legs Mme Marie-Fran\u00e7oise C\u00f4te, accept\u00e9 par d\u00e9cret du 9 juillet 1961","jabachInventory":"","napoleonInventory":"","previousOwner":[{"value":"Mme C\u00f4te, Marie-Fran\u00e7oise","note":"","role":", Donateur"},{"value":"M. C\u00f4te, Claudius","note":"","role":", Collectionneur"}],"acquisitionDetails":[{"mode":"legs","doubt":"","dates":[{"type":"date du legs","value":"1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date de comit\u00e9\/commission","value":"02\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du conseil","value":"16\/02\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961},{"type":"date du d\u00e9cret","value":"09\/07\/1961","startYear":1961,"endYear":1961}]}],"ownedBy":"Etat","heldBy":"Mus\u00e9e du Louvre, D\u00e9partement des Objets d\u0027art du Moyen Age,